    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/458d9be0a72d95ac63434c63ae0bba9f.poster.avif?t=1743957072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/458d9be0a72d95ac63434c63ae0bba9f.webm?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/458d9be0a72d95ac63434c63ae0bba9f.mp4?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你想为王国寻回昔日的光辉还是要将其推番自立为王呢？新增版包括《堕落军团；王国之罪篇》及《堕落军团：逆军之炎篇》两个游戏。<br><br>在《堕落军团；王国之罪篇》Cecille公主带同身世成谜的魔法书出发去拯救正在瓦解的家园。而在《堕落军团：逆军之炎篇》Laendur将军将率领同盟夺回在王国失去的一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/04053d02bae4d8d54b260fe204acaf07.poster.avif?t=1743957072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/04053d02bae4d8d54b260fe204acaf07.webm?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/04053d02bae4d8d54b260fe204acaf07.mp4?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>玩家须要带领被赋予生命化身为士兵的武器并纯熟运用连续技以击败强大的敌人。除了要应付激烈战事外，玩家还要在激战前的瞬间为国家作出困难的抉择并承担其后果。你会要胁某王子增强士兵的能力？还是要向饥饿的村民征收赋税来换取随行士兵的性命？每个决定会提升玩家不同能力的同时，也会改变故事的发展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/d162ecadc777b316e325649560943cdb.poster.avif?t=1743957072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/d162ecadc777b316e325649560943cdb.webm?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612820/extras/d162ecadc777b316e325649560943cdb.mp4?t=1743957072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >同一战事，两个角度</h2>《堕落军团》新增版让你从两个不同角度更深入了解Fenumia王国。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的军团，尽在你的掌控之中</h2>玩家可以同时操控四名角色，纯熟运用连续技，看准时机抵抗并向敌人作出反击。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的每个决定均会改变王国的命运</h2>玩家须于数秒间作出统治决定，每个决定均会影响故事的发展。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >画风优美</h2>游戏内的每个画面均是手绘图，上至重要人物如来势汹汹的怪兽，下至不明显的细节如城墙上的砖块我们也没有忽略仔细的绘画出来。",
